{"tid":187231,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要點先可以唔會咁易呷醋？？？","createTime":"2017-04-04T19:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T21:30:56.000Z","uid":91908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3970f383f66cb10c3365ee445a8c4e59120e60c5","tid":187231,"uid":91908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:37:00.000Z","msg":"我以前拍拖 都唔太介意ex女啊去玩咁 <br />\n好似無乜特別感覺 亦唔會點呷醋<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解對住現任 就變得超易呷醋<br />\n因為啲小事 我個心都會變得好妒忌好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見有部分絲打都唔介意男朋友女啊同女仔傾計啊等等<br />\n<br />\n究竟點先可以做到唔呷醋？<br />\n<br />\n定還是我太愛現任先會咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90a5b568dc21508d40cf24a84398d971265cb6f","tid":187231,"uid":90706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:47:14.000Z","msg":"定係對自己太冇自信"},{"pid":"04da496cd3aee4c8e2763e5c4bceef2e573f2e0b","tid":187231,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:57:28.000Z","msg":"好易呷醋<br />\n所以男友唔會睇女<br />\n剩係睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b807b9d1dd3dc0bcc69ae36c3bde7d2d7143109","tid":187231,"uid":91908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:59:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定係對自己太冇自信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啊 呢個都係其中一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我就係唔明點解以前拍拖又唔會呷醋 因為我好似根本唔係太care對方會唔會俾人搶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但反而今次我就好驚無左佢 <br />\n驚到好小事就會呷醋會亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91540931c568841b2ff5757fa5762b2bdfabf3ea","tid":187231,"uid":91908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好易呷醋<br />\n所以男友唔會睇女<br />\n剩係睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a86c6a9989e66134bad4c94d024b3d091c94523","tid":187231,"uid":90706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>定係對自己太冇自信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啊 呢個都係其中一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我就係唔明點解以前拍拖又唔會呷醋 因為我好似根本唔係太care對方會唔會俾人搶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但反而今次我就好驚無左佢 <br />\n驚到好小事就會呷醋會亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到尾 今次遇到個食住妳嘅人 妳咪算執到lor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n 嘖係妳的確好鍾意對方 <br />\n以前果d 充其量係水泡，為拍拖而拍拖<br />\n<br />\n既然係甘，絲打應該同對方好好傾傾 比如話如果可以 應該儘量唔好做某d行為，妳會開心d <br />\n如果對方個心有妳， 應該都可以有一定改進"},{"pid":"23b08c07e8d088ce10817ca26b609a09c6b0f6e2","tid":187231,"uid":91908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>定係對自己太冇自信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啊 呢個都係其中一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我就係唔明點解以前拍拖又唔會呷醋 因為我好似根本唔係太care對方會唔會俾人搶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但反而今次我就好驚無左佢 <br />\n驚到好小事就會呷醋會亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到尾 今次遇到個食住妳嘅人 妳咪算執到lor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n 嘖係妳的確好鍾意對方 <br />\n以前果d 充其量係水泡，為拍拖而拍拖<br />\n<br />\n既然係<span style=\"color: red;\">甘</span>，絲打應該同對方好好傾傾 比如話如果可以 應該儘量唔好做某d行為，妳會開心d <br />\n如果對方個心有妳， 應該都可以有一定改進</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係多謝你嘅意見啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過循例提返你係「咁」唔係「甘」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f570b636db460f20e48ed4bb8f5bbc6f36788a64","tid":187231,"uid":